## Common Standard Fields

These fields appear in multiple standard objects:

| Field API Name | Description | Objects |
|---------------|-------------|---------|
| Id | Unique identifier for the record | All Objects |
| Name | Primary name field | Most Objects |
| CreatedDate | Date and time when the record was created | All Objects |
| CreatedById | ID of the user who created the record | All Objects |
| LastModifiedDate | Date and time when the record was last modified | All Objects |
| LastModifiedById | ID of the user who last modified the record | All Objects |
| SystemModstamp | Date and time when the record was last modified by a user or by an automated process | All Objects |
| IsDeleted | Indicates whether the record has been moved to the Recycle Bin (true) or not (false) | All Objects |
| OwnerId | ID of the assigned owner of the record | Most Objects |
| LastActivityDate | Date of the last activity (task, event) logged on the record | Many Objects |

